				<td colspan="2"><span>yes, the gear these items appear on sans aug is higher end GoD; however, keep in mind the difficulty of the combine compared with the extreme rarity of the components.
<br />

<br />
Ench - jc
<br />
Shm-Alch
<br />
Rogue (maybe..who trusts a rogue)
<br />

<br />
20 hours for (1) lightning core in MPG
<br />
60-70AA and 5 levels in WoS--1 discordant Scoriae
<br />
Have yet to see a slug worm...
<br />

<br />
The augs themselves are NOT bad to get. It's the components that are simply insane to get.
<br />

<br />
To add::
<br />
assume 100 hours or so PER discordant scoriae drop, per 6 players in WoS.  30ish people in the zone at any given time that means about 1 scoriae drops per day maybe 2.  just from that zone.  So assuming the same # of people in the other 3-4 zones, you can figure on 8-12 serverwide per day.
<br />

<br />
Of those even max crafted folks will fail 1/3 of the time.  So one -3 augsCOULD (possibly) be MADE successfully per day (possibly).
<br />

<br />
How rare are they meant to be?</span></td>
