Having seen how rare discordant scoriae were, I decided to go for the focusII affects and have 3 now (my rog friend failed on marking a citrine and 1 inlay).
<br />
I cut the stones myself (succeeded on 1/6 radiant, 3/3 brilliant and 2/2 polished at 252 JC) and made the inlay (only failed once on white gold inlay with 252 smithing).
